                                <p>An Income Tax Return (ITR) is a form used to file information about your income and tax to the Income Tax Department. It is mandatory for individuals and businesses to file ITR if their income exceeds a certain limit, or if they meet specific criteria. Filing ITR helps in claiming refunds, carrying forward losses, and is often required for loan or visa applications.</p>
